💁🏻‍♂️So check this out! We had the super fun opportunity to transform a basic garage into a family dream space… all to raise money for scholarships!
.
☝🏻Make sure to take note of the #pingpongtable 🍻 too 😂 #summerisstillhere☀️
.
🙋🏻‍♂️I’m so thankful for our amazing partners in this 👏🏻:

- @serenaandlily for those great furnishings
- @180closetdesign for all that clever storage
- @sarah_klein_santa_cruz for loads of beautiful textiles
- @carolinepaculaprints for the gorgeous art

#showhouse #magazine #dreamgarage 🏡By: @christiandawdesign @aspiredesignandhome @harrisondesign @artisan_builders @claybornetravis @sherwinwilliams @mathews.terri 📸 @ronbluntphoto
